      "content": "okay i get the reye's syndrome thing but is it really that dangerous if it's just a one time thing? he's really suffering and honestly the tylenol we have is almost empty and i don't want to drive to the pharmacy at 2am. can i just give him a baby aspirin or something similar? it's better than him staying this miserable isnt it?",
